definitions.definition: ( science fiction ) In Star Trek , a Starfleet commander and science officer of the USS Enterprise , especially known for his Vulcan logic, reason , and stoicism and his distinctive pointed ears.
Ellipsis of 2309 Mr. Spock : an asteroid in the main belt , Solar System .

definitions.definition: A person or character like a Star Trek Vulcan ; someone resembling Star Trek ' s character Spock.
The Vulcan salute when used in rock-paper-scissors-lizard-Spock , a handshape that beats rock and scissors and loses to lizard and paper .
